{
  "stem": "26142.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But it was a very dark, pitch dark night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We run to the highway.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "In meantime-- in the meantime, we realize, we-- three of us, Moshe and the children, are not here.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So we started running back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And while we were running back, we met up, we met up with them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then we realized that we left everything-- we left everything there, whatever we had, in those-- so we-- we told Moshe and Monte, well, the-- the screams.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Where is [NON-ENGLISH.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] was missing until they found him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we told them to stay here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We are going back, [NON-ENGLISH] and I will go back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We run back and fortunately we found our packages, we grabbed them, and we started running back to the highway.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And while we were already the six of us together, we took-- and-- and-- and and-- and-- and fortunately the kids were not hit and they were so quiet.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They were so quiet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Up to this day, I can't understand it, how these children, they knew something is wrong in all this.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we started to run back of the same highway from where we came.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "How-- we ran for a few minutes until we had to stop and to catch our breath until we noticed-- from far away we noticed, that there is a barn on the field.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we decided we are going.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And here, we are only the six of us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The three brothers, my sister-in-law and the two children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We are going and tried to go into this-- to this barn.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We saw a house there, a barn.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we came in there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The barn was open.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, it was-- it wasn't locked.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were able to open it up and we came in.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
